| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3173 — Recovery Inhibition (vicesociety)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ad64c719-3b91-5ef7-81f6-ca01e36cbf23"
